title: Reboot customer's computer
buttons: custendprobticket: Didn't work - file a ticket, conclude: Worked

<p>We are showing no problems with our service.</p>

<p>There may be a problem with the settings on your computer, or a program running that's preventing you from accessing the Internet.</p>

<p>Please restart your computer.  The way to do this depends on your system, but usually there's an item for it in the Start menu.<br/>
<span class="dont-say">If the customer can't figure out how to restart their computer, click "Didn't work - File a ticket".</span></p>

<p class="dont-say">Wait for the customer's computer to reboot.</p>

